title: 02/14/22 DPS Hour 1 Ross Tucker
itunes:title: 02/14/22 DPS Hour 1 Ross Tucker
description:
In hour 1 of the Dan Patrick Show, the crew recaps the Super Bowl. Dan Patrick questions if its possible the Rams found a new blueprint for getting to the big game. Who was more deserving of the MVP, Aaron Donald or Cooper Kupp. Joe Burrow being a little MIA during the 2nd half and Ross Tucker joins to give his take on the season finale.
